platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Building upon 2Ks tactical masterpiece XCOM: Enemy Unknown, Enemy Within adds a bevy of new features that fundamentally alter and improve the experience. With new abilities and mission parameters unlocked from the very first mission, Enemy Within injects tension and surprise into every corner. Fans of Enemy Unknown will find a wealth of new weapons, enemies, and maps that change the games flow, while new players will be enthralled as they fend off an alien invasion in intense, turn-based battles.
